item.title: Overview
item.description: Label Convert link A dataset format conversion tool for object detection and image segmentation, which supports mutual conversion between labelme, labelImg tools and YOLO, VOC, and COCO dataset formats. Transformation Diagram linkInstallation link pip install label_convert Contributing linkPull requests are welcome. For major changes, please open an issue first to discuss what you would like to change. Please make sure to update tests as appropriate. License linkApache 2.0
